name: FNF Hi Engine: Vs. Maccus.ERR
description:
Hi already beat Maccus.EXE in a rap battle once, but it isn't over yet; he's in his newest form now, Maccus.ERR!!

Rap battle against Maccus.ERR and Soul Rex in this FNF game!

Use WASD or the arrow keys to play.

HUGE thanks to ToyManTomyJNR on Scratch for ths Hi Engine.

Note: The end of the song Toxin is extremely loud. Turn down your volume.

Another Note: this game will not be updated.
